videoSnippet.title: Most Amazing Attacking Game - Grischuk vs MVL on Chess.com
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Grischuk Knocks Out MVL In 1st Speed Chess Upset

Alexander Grischuk eliminated Maxime Vachier-Lagrave in the MasterClass Speed Chess Champioship's first quarterfinal. Grischuk's next opponent is the winner of the match between Magnus Carlsen and Wesley So.

Grischuk (2875) vs. LyonBeast (2799)
Live Chess | Chess.com | 23 Oct 2017

1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 d6 3. f4 Nc6 4. Nf3 g6 5. Bc4 Bg7 6. O-O e6 7. d4 Nxd4 8. Be3 Nxf3+ 9. Qxf3 Ne7 10. Rad1 O-O 11. Bxc5 Qc7 12. Bxd6 Qxc4 13. Bxe7 Re8 14. e5 Rxe7 15. Rd8+ Bf8 16. Ne4 Kg7 17. Nf6 Qxc2 18. Qh3 h5 19. Qg3 Qf5 20. Rfd1 b6 21. Rxf8 Kxf8 22. Rd8+ Kg7 23. Rg8+ Kh6 24. h4
